name: MORNING DEPARTURE RUSH! Montreal (YUL) Airport Runway 06R (4K)
description:
Thank you to RadarBox for supporting this plane spotting video! Find out more about them at https://www.radarbox.com/?referrer=AlexAviation

Montreal's Trudeau Airport is the busiest one in Quebec, and is home to Air Canada. Even in August 2021, the morning rush features some fantastic traffic, with plenty of heavy aircraft departing. Please enjoy this compilation of traffic taking off from runway 06R!

With thanks to @MarkBrandonAviation
